  "3111980": {
    "name": "The Green Way: Farming Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3111980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to <strong>The Green Way</strong>, </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >where your farming dreams come to life! Experience the journey from both <strong>first-person and third-person perspectives</strong>, switching freely to play the way you prefer. Begin with a modest plot of land and grow it into a thriving agricultural empire. Plant and harvest crops, care for livestock, and sell your produce to build wealth and earn your place in the community. Farming is only the start—step into an immersive world where every choice you make shapes your success and your lifestyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Key Features:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Farm Management</strong>: Plant and harvest a variety of crops, manage livestock, and optimize your farm for maximum efficiency - while staying prepared to handle unexpected accidents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Business Expansion</strong>: Expand your holdings by purchasing more land and increasing your production capabilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Market and Shop Management</strong>: Sell your goods at local markets or open your own shop. Negotiate prices and build relationships with customers to grow your reputation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Home and Lifestyle</strong>: Upgrade your farmhouse, purchase vehicles, and decorate with luxurious items as your wealth grows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Land Customization</strong>: Buy building plots, design your land, and construct houses, walls, towers, markets, and more. Create a personalized and unique farmstead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Community Engagement</strong>: Interact with neighbors, participate in festivals, and contribute to the local economy to become a respected member of the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements and Challenges</strong>: Complete challenges and earn achievements that showcase your farming prowess and business acumen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create Your Legacy</strong>: From a small-time farmer to a magnate of agriculture, forge your path in The Green Way. Explore, expand, and experience the joys and challenges of rural life as you build a legacy that will be remembered for generations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>-Some Gameplay Features GIFs - :</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Farming Lifecycle System:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/17d5d9e0c773d826359b1d806398ee15.poster.avif?t=1768237086\" width=784 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/17d5d9e0c773d826359b1d806398ee15.webm?t=1768237086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/17d5d9e0c773d826359b1d806398ee15.mp4?t=1768237086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/6bb8706ef228e5e187e15b37f7c5cda8.poster.avif?t=1768237086\" width=784 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/6bb8706ef228e5e187e15b37f7c5cda8.webm?t=1768237086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/6bb8706ef228e5e187e15b37f7c5cda8.mp4?t=1768237086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong></strong><br><br><br><br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">-  <br><strong>In-Game Economy</strong> <strong>System:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/cfad8789512b084ec0a3ca73ebc961f1.poster.avif?t=1768237086\" width=784 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/cfad8789512b084ec0a3ca73ebc961f1.webm?t=1768237086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/cfad8789512b084ec0a3ca73ebc961f1.mp4?t=1768237086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/eafc316d0a5523a1101f485a04a167a8.poster.avif?t=1768237086\" width=788 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/eafc316d0a5523a1101f485a04a167a8.webm?t=1768237086\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3111980/extras/eafc316d0a5523a1101f485a04a167a8.mp4?t=1768237086\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.a